It is not you, Airy, it is me. You see... although I do not remember my past, I still can feel something in my heart. I know, I... I feel that I love another person and that she waits even now for me! But I cannot remember where she is or how to find her. You are a very nice girl, Airy, but I will neither cheat you nor anyone else. And please, do not do any more foolish things. Next time I may not arrive in time.
